metadata.name: Rekter #1
metadata.description: The Rekters are the long-time enemies of the Nifties. After they were forced to leave The Nifty Way Galaxy for their conflicting attitude, they’ve been wandering around the Ethereum universe planning their revenge. Now that they found out that more than 4000 Nifties live happily in Planet Earth, they are ready t invade the Wallets of all those true Holders and take over our Planet. It’s time to protect the most precious NFT in the Universe, our Planet Earth… Nifty, are you ready for the battle?
